Package photoAlbum.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    Album object that contains list of photos and information on the number of photos, oldest photo, and newest photo
    Photo
    Photo object with information on the photo's date, caption, tags, and associated album.
    Tag
    Tag object that contains information on a list of photos that include this tag
    User
    User class that contains username and password, all of user's albums, and lists of photos in the user's albums that contain certain tags.
